@startuml wlan_ground_truth_pipeline
title WLAN Ground-Truth Test Infrastructure Data Flow

participant "Fixture Corpus" as FC
participant "Layer 1: Audit" as L1
participant "CLI: enrich-fixtures" as CLI
participant "Layer 2: Backend\nReconciliation" as L2
participant "Layer 3: Ground-Truth\nVerification" as L3
participant "CI/Report" as CI

== Input Stage ==
FC -> FC: test/fixtures/wlan/\n{api,struct,ring,...}/*.json\nManifest: index.json

== Completeness Audit (Layer 1) ==
FC -> L1: Load all fixtures\n60 APIs + 11 families
L1 -> L1: Count relation buckets\nper fixture (Tier 1/2/3)
L1 -> FC: Output:\ncompleteness-audit.json\n(per_api_scores[], tier_distribution)

== Enrichment Pipeline ==
FC -> CLI: npm run enrich:fixtures
CLI -> CLI: Load fixture +\nWLAN workspace source +\nquery backend
CLI -> FC: Write:\nupdate fixture relations +\nbackup .pre-enrich

== Backend Reconciliation (Layer 2) ==
FC -> L2: Load fixture relations\n(protocol edge_kind format)
L2 -> L2: fixtureRelationsToMockRows():\ntranslate protocol→DB edge_kind\nemit 2 mock rows per relation
L2 -> L2: setIntelligenceDeps():\ninject mock DB rows
L2 -> L2: Execute intent from\nFAMILY_INTENTS[family]
L2 -> L2: Compare response items\nvs. fixture by\n(canonical_name,\nfile_path, line_number)
L2 -> L2: Validate relation buckets,\nedge_kinds match contract

== Ground-Truth Verification (Layer 3) ==
FC -> L3: Load wlan-ground-truth.json:\nverification targets +\nquery cases + mock rows
L3 -> L3: Per-API verification:\nexplicit relation contracts\nquery intent coverage
L3 -> L3: Validate source anchors\n(if WLAN_WORKSPACE_ROOT)

== Output & CI ==
L1 -> CI: Audit report:\nper_api_scores,\napis_needing_followup
L2 -> CI: Reconciliation mismatches:\nmissing/extra/mismatch items
L3 -> CI: Verification results:\npass/fail per intent
CI -> CI: [MISSING]\nUnified comparator:\nclassify mismatch types\nUnified report (JSON+MD)\nConfidence scoring\nTrend tracking\nCI threshold enforcement

note right of CI
  Current gaps:
  1. No classified mismatch taxonomy
  2. No unified comparator output
  3. No confidence aggregation
  4. No trend tracking
  5. No CI integration/thresholds
end note

@enduml
